{
  "stem": "26699.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, on the 29th of June, 1941, in the morning, we had shootings in the street.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were living on the central street, on the second-- on the first floor of a block of flats.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were shoutings and people crying and rushing and running here in the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my mother said, there is a pogrom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't know what the pogrom is, but this was what she reckoned that is going to be.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The first measure she took, she locked the front door of the flat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were living in a two bedroom flat with a little lounge.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the three of us-- my father, my mother, myself-- we went under the bed to hide ourselves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It didn't pass longer than half an hour, and strong blows on the front door came.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But the door was strong, it didn't break.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we heard blows like an ax, and the door was opened then.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The three of us were in hiding under the bed with a bedcloth above.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "A man rushed in, and he was Enache, E-N-A-C-H-E, the caretaker of the block of flats.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was the one with the ax, who broke the door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And swearing around, [SPEAKING ROMANIAN], it's where this bloody Jews run away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because he couldn't see us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But he want probably just to kill us with his ax and loot the flat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he was very upset that he couldn't find us to split our skulls with his ax.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But he was just a petty criminal.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
